00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:50,000
Paul tells us,

338
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:50,360
doesn't he,

339
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:52,680
that he was a Hebrew-speaking Jew,

340
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:55,600
that he was a Torah-observant Pharisee.

341
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:57,160
He tells us that in Philippians.

342
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:58,800
So he knew the scriptures.

343
00:10:58,800 --> 00:11:00,080
He probably chewed masses

344
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,840
of the Old Testament by heart.

345
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:02,960
So therefore,

346
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:05,360
he knew about the God of hope

