00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:22,960
that we're just going to look at

356
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:23,880
in a moment,

357
00:11:23,880 --> 00:11:25,280
to multiple scriptures.

358
00:11:25,280 --> 00:11:26,000
He would have believed

