00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:36,080
and then ultimately would come

366
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:37,600
a new heaven and a new earth,

367
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:38,840
which he would have read about

368
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:39,560
in Isaiah.

369
00:11:39,560 --> 00:11:41,520
And if you were to ask

370
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:42,800
the same question

371
00:11:42,800 --> 00:11:44,400
to Saul of Tarsus

