00:12:16,760 --> 00:12:18,080
written in the past,

393
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:18,840
and of course he means

394
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,000
the scriptures of what we call

395
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:20,720
the Old Testament,

396
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:22,640
was written to teach us

397
00:12:22,640 --> 00:12:24,360
so that through the endurance

