Paul says the whole Old Testament

403
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:32,000
was to give us hope.

404
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:33,360
Have you ever thought of that?

405
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:34,640
The Old Testament

406
00:12:34,640 --> 00:12:35,560
gives you a lot of problems

407
00:12:35,560 --> 00:12:36,600
and a lot of classes

408
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,400
and a lot of exams

