00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:29,080
that was so that

452
00:13:29,080 --> 00:13:30,200
all nations,

453
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:31,000
the Gentiles,

454
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,280
would come to find

455
00:13:32,280 --> 00:13:32,800
their hope

