00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:44,760
And then,

466
00:13:44,760 --> 00:13:45,880
in order to

467
00:13:45,880 --> 00:13:47,120
reinforce that

468
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:48,520
climactic point,

469
00:13:48,520 --> 00:13:48,920
which is,

470
00:13:48,920 --> 00:13:49,600
let's remember that

471
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:51,200
Romans 15

