00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:06,000
his intention,

484
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:07,200
from chapter 1,

485
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:07,960
was to bring about

486
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:09,120
the obedience of faith

487
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:10,000
among the nations.

488
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:11,080
That's what the Gospel

489
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:11,760
is all about.

