00:15:03,360 --> 00:15:05,040
hope for the nations,

534
00:15:05,040 --> 00:15:06,320
is the climax

535
00:15:06,320 --> 00:15:07,200
of the Book of Romans,

536
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:09,040
because Jesus of Nazareth

537
00:15:09,040 --> 00:15:10,680
has fulfilled the promises

538
00:15:10,680 --> 00:15:12,240
of the Old Testament Scriptures,

539
00:15:12,240 --> 00:15:14,320
and the mercy

540
00:15:14,320 --> 00:15:15,320
and the glory of God

541
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:16,480
is now going to the ends

542
00:15:16,480 --> 00:15:17,200
of the earth.

543
00:15:17,200 --> 00:15:19,280
That vision is now being fulfilled

544
00:15:19,280 --> 00:15:21,120
through Christ and his victory.

545
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:22,400
And it's being extended

546
00:15:22,400 --> 00:15:23,800
to every sinner

547
00:15:23,800 --> 00:15:25,160
and to all nations

548
00:15:25,160 --> 00:15:26,400
and indeed to the whole

549
00:15:26,400 --> 00:15:27,160
of creation.

