00:15:57,920 --> 00:15:59,240
of course, to the big problem

571
00:15:59,240 --> 00:15:59,760
that we have,

572
00:15:59,760 --> 00:16:01,200
which is in Genesis 3,

573
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:03,400
which is because we chose

574
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:04,440
in Adam and Eve

575
00:16:04,440 --> 00:16:06,440
to distrust and disobey God

576
00:16:06,760 --> 00:16:08,200
The result was sin, evil

577
00:16:08,200 --> 00:16:08,680
and death

578
00:16:08,680 --> 00:16:10,880
