579
00:16:10,880 --> 00:16:12,160
to every dimension

580
00:16:12,160 --> 00:16:13,800
of the human personality.

581
00:16:13,800 --> 00:16:15,840
It's remarkable

582
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:17,480
in that little story there

583
00:16:17,480 --> 00:16:19,120
in Genesis chapter 3

584
00:16:19,120 --> 00:16:22,320
of how when Eve is,

585
00:16:22,320 --> 00:16:23,640
you know, confronted

586
00:16:23,640 --> 00:16:24,720
by this temptation

587
00:16:24,720 --> 00:16:25,520
from the serpent

588
00:16:25,520 --> 00:16:28,400
that the evil

