in Colossians 1:15-20.

1236
00:31:06,960 --> 00:31:08,520
That marvelous passage

1237
00:31:08,520 --> 00:31:09,200
where Paul,

1238
00:31:09,200 --> 00:31:10,520
it's just incredible

1239
00:31:10,520 --> 00:31:11,120
what he says.

